  _story: 'As a Technical Producer at Meta, Neil was responsible for the health of
    4 of the top 10 live service games on the Oculus Quest Store. As AI tools became
    readily available, Neil set up realtime monitoring and alerts for DAU, conversion
    rates, and spending to flag any anomolies for both himself and the external Lead
    Producers.


    By taking a data driven approach, issues were caught and addressed
    in near real time.


    Bonus: Schedule an interview with Neil and he may tell
    you about how he convinced a developer to NOT to implement a certain feature
    in the game.'
